description.en:
The Family of Mewn lived through several millennium’s, surviving wars north and south. Losing most of the family name through the bloodbath one lone survivor Mewn Inu was born! 
 
Born on the 1st of the 11th 2021 ( 111 ) Mewn has a main goal of growing and expanding its family and saving the family name.
 
A few common enemies are the families of dogs, the empire of doge and shiba have great threats to the Mewn kingdom but the community and people are ready to fight and give it what it takes to grow and conquer.
 
To join the fight all you have to do is buy some Mewn on ERC20 and you then become part of the family, and it gets even simpler, the job as soldiers of the community is to shill on all socials and expand and grow this beautiful kingdom of Mewn
 
Long live our prince Mewn
